@node "glossary" "MUILabeler - Glossary"
   @{b}AUISG@{ub}
         The Amiga User Interface Style Guide (AUISG) provides a standard
         for the look and behavior of Amiga software.  MUILabeler attempts
         to conform to the AUISG whenever possible (and practical).

   @{b}Magic User Interface@{ub}
         MagicUserInterface (or MUI) is the system responsible for the
         layout and appearance of MUILabeler's visual interface.  MUI is
         copyright 1993 Stefan Stuntz.  MUILabeler requires MUI 2.0 or
         above.
         See @{" Magic User Interface " link "mui"}.

   @{b}MUI@{ub}
         See @{b}Magic User Interface@{ub}.
@endnode
